entries.femaleVariant: I keep thinking about that house. And that hallway. It was so dark, and those strange voices, and that cold air...
<kiroshi l="rus" o="Всё в этой стране не слава богу. Даже архитектура." t="Everything in this country is fucked up. Even the architecture." b="" a=""/>
But that hallway shouldn't have been there! I saw the blueprints! Maybe... maybe the house was haunted?
